clinic.name: Inglewood Family Dental
clinic.description: Dr. Arash Ravanbakhsh and the team of Calgary dentists are dedicated to giving you proper dental care. You have the convenience of open evenings/ extended evening hours and open Sundays. We follow the 2024 ADA Fee Guide for all of our invoices, and we offer direct billing for most insurance plans. Set up an appointment if you are searching for a dentist near you, near Bridgeland, Memorial Drive, Crescent Heights, Sunnyside, and downtown. Our dentist in Calgary is looking forward to meeting you, and all new patients are welcome! Our multilingual dental office has financing options available, senior discount/ seniors receive discounts on all treatments, and free teeth whitening, cosmetic, and therapeutic botox treatments are provided.
